  "texts": [
    "Vicuna shows considerable underperformance in comparison.",
    "Briva-Iglesias, Vicent; João Lucas Cavalheiro Camargo & Gokhan Dogru",
    "After presenting the results of the AEMs, this section presents the HE scores, so we can triangulate the data and discern which is the MT system that provides the best MT output in the legal domain for the languages analysed.",
